thread.title: Gil

author: Gil
title: Gil
text:
It's exciting to actually put the trees in the ground. I recently purchased a vast selection of fruit trees and fruit bushes for a house I just purchased. Paw-Paw, Olive, Banana, are just a few things I found at Willis Orchard (that on one else had) and put in the ground.
I'll keep you guys posted with the growth. When you plant a fruit tree you are truly contributing to everyone's future.
